== USER GOALS ==
Deploy DB changes separated by pre- and post- application deployment
* migrate schema adds
* separately deploy new application code
* migrate schema drops

Rollback DB changes, including items that were dropped

Segregate DB changes by "release", to limit how far a rollback can go

Support various types of migrations:
* add/drop table
* add/drop column
* add/drop stored procedure
* add/drop view
* add/drop index
* add/drop constraint
* grant/revoke

